                    p.text-muted We put farming first&mdash;developing new techniques to be the most efficient and most responsible we can
                .col-md-4
                    span.fa-stack.fa-4x
                        i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
                        i.fa.fa-thumbs-up.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
                    h4.service-heading Advocates
                    p.text-muted We care about entomophagy not only for our own benefit, but for the benefit of the planet
